title: The Beatles - The Ultimate Live Beatles Collection - 23 cds
description: Here we have the Ultimate Beatles Live Anthology. This was originally a 25 cd box-set, but the offically released tracks (Hollywood Bowl) have been removed so this could be shared on bootleg sites without legal issues :) Please enjoy, share with friends and PLEASE seed for a while, i need your help. Same for the hundreds of other uploads i did, do not hit and run but leave your computer running for a while. O, and be kind, download maximum 3 or 4 of my uploads at the same time, not 10 or 20 simultanuously... ================================================== The Beatles - The Ultimate Live Beatles Collection (Coltturkey) Here is my idea of an upgrade of the Great Purple Chick Live Chronicle Series. So many years are gone since them and many new upgrades are coming to light. Fab Production had done an good upgrade, but the Fab Collection are a few years from now and we have find more at the time.(Coltturkey) Volume 01 - Scream As Loud As You Can - July 1957 - October 1963 Volume 02 - The rest of you just rattle your jewellery November - November 1963 - December 1963 Volume 03 - Have Some Fun Tonight - January 1964 - February 1964 Volume 04 - Shut up! Paulie's Talking - February 1964 Volume 05 - A Midsummer Night's Dream - April 1964 Volume 06 - Best wishes, Jimmy Nichol - June 1964 Volume 07 - Back With Us Now, Ringo - June 1964 Volume 08 - In The Eye of the Hurricane - June 1964 - August 1964 Volume 09 - Great To Have You With Us - August 1964 [REMOVED - INCLUDES HOLLYWOOD BOWL] Volume 10 - Stamp Out Detroit - September 1964 Volume 11 - Baby's in Blackpool - September 1964 - April 1965 Volume 12 - Et Maintenant, Une Chanson - June 1965 Volume 13 - Opportunity Knocks - June 1965 - July 1965 Volume 14 - Can You Hear Me. - August 1965 Volume 15 - Howdy Y'all! - August 1965 Volume 16 - Thank You Very Much For Coming - August 1965 Volume 17 - Reelin' And Rockin' - August 1965 [REMOVED - INCLUDES HOLLYWOOD BOWL] Volume 18 - Mach Schau - June 1966 Volume 19 - Big In Japan - June - July 1966 Volume 20 - More Popular Than Jesus - August 1966 Volume 21 - Here Come The Beatles - August 1966 Volume 22 - Don't Make it Bad Volume 23 - I hope we've passed the audition Volume 24 - Live At the Madison Square Garden ZU LAUT SPECIAL EDITION STEREO Full artwork for all cd's included, sample below: https://imgur.com/W9N1aqx https://imgur.com/7dtuRuA
